    "We included PubMed database because our pilot research showed that much of the work in RAI was originated, applied, or linked to healthcare.",
    "These databases were selected primarily to achieve the objective of our review.",
    "We excluded databases that did not directly align with our review's interdisciplinary scope or if their content substantially overlapped with the chosen databases.",
    "For example, IEEE Xplore was judged as having a narrower focus on engineering and computing, which is already covered by the ACM digital library.",
    "Similarly, Web of Science was considered but excluded due to significant overlap with Scopus.The inclusion criteria used to select relevant articles and their justification can be found in Table 2."
